## 🛠️ Installation Steps

1. Clone the repository

```Bash
git clone https://github.com/Rohit19060/kings_clock_2.git
```

2. Go into the Project Directory

3. Install dependencies

```Bash
flutter pub get
```

4. Run the app

```Bash
flutter run/Flutter run --release
```
